# Optional override for the Microsoft Power BI Modeling MCP bridge.
# Setup scripts prefer the native Microsoft binary for the current OS:
# - macOS arm64: node_modules/@microsoft/powerbi-modeling-mcp-darwin-arm64/dist/powerbi-modeling-mcp
# - macOS x64: node_modules/@microsoft/powerbi-modeling-mcp-darwin-x64/dist/powerbi-modeling-mcp
# - Windows x64: node_modules\@microsoft\powerbi-modeling-mcp-win32-x64\dist\powerbi-modeling-mcp.exe
# Fallback default: npx -y @microsoft/powerbi-modeling-mcp@latest --start --authmode=interactive
# POWERBI_MODELING_MCP_COMMAND=npx
# POWERBI_MODELING_MCP_ARGS=-y @microsoft/powerbi-modeling-mcp@latest --start --authmode=interactive

# Optional CEO defaults. Known workspaces avoid needing tenant-wide REST discovery.
# POWERBI_KNOWN_WORKSPACES=test-mcp,finance,hospital
# POWERBI_DEFAULT_WORKSPACE=test-mcp
# POWERBI_DEFAULT_SEMANTIC_MODEL=hospital

# Optional output folder for generated HTML executive reports.
# Defaults to ./powerbi-report-output from the MCP server process cwd.
# POWERBI_REPORT_OUTPUT_DIR=/Users/ducna/powerbi-report-output
